data.description: 418 BILBO ... A STUNNING FUSION OF HISTORIC & MODERN ... This restored beauty evokes a cottage vibe and sits in the cultural hub of DeRidder. Begin YOUR new story here.  YOUR KEYS are waiting with a $3,000.00 buyer paid closing costs concession!
